*   ## **_WOMENS TAG TEAN CHAMPIONSHIPS: JADE CARGILL AND BIANCA BELAIR DEF. INDI HARTWELL AND CANDICE LERAE_**
    

Jade and Bianca are using Adam Cole and Kyle O'Reilly old Wheelbarrow Suplex combo as a finish. Pretty cool.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/eff7e688-a0ad-414d-b2c1-48afb9569f3e/20240525_100905.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WWE WOMEN'S WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: LIV MORGAN DEF. BECKY LYNCH(C)_**
    

Great back and forth action to open the show. Midway through, the story shifts as Dominik Mysterio appears to distract Becky

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/92b436ac-cb6a-4acb-ada6-e3d90da805f5/20240525_102539.jpg?format=original)

Dom slides a chair into the ring. Distracts the ref as Liv DDTs Becky onto the chair and wins the Women's World Championship!!!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ab6c71b7-67a0-493c-babf-7730614d35ea/20240525_103621.jpg?format=original)

The crowd is showering Chad Gable with YOU SUCK chants, synced to his theme song.

Gable forces Maxxine to leave. He has a plan with Otis tonight

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0d34ed81-4821-414e-9d60-0559f4756e9d/20240525_105741.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WWE INTERCONTINENTAL CHAMPIONSHIP: SAMI ZAYN DEF. CHAD GABLE AND BRONSON REED_**
    

EXCELLENT, PPV Quality triple threat match. Chad Gable tries to get Otis to interfere and Otis fights with himself but he attacks anyway AND TAKES OUT CHAD GABLE BY ACCIDENT.

Sami rolls into the ring and finishes off Bronson Reed.

